name: insomnia-plugin-ulid-generator
author: Caio Ferreira
description: Insomnia plugin for generating unique, lexicographically sortable identifiers (ULID). Useful for creating test data and unique identifiers in API requests.

insomnia.name: ulid-generator
insomnia.description: Generate ULIDs (Universally Unique Lexicographically Sortable Identifiers) for testing and unique identifiers in API requests.
